  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4 \u0daf\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7, \u0dad\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0dbd\u0db6\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One person is killed and three injured in a shooting in Rathgama in broad daylight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, one person was killed and three others were injured in a shooting that took place in Rathgama today (31st).",
        "This shooting was done by two unknown gunmen who came to a house in Rathgama.",
        "A person who was seriously injured due to gunshot died on the spot and three other injured people were taken to the hospital.",
        "Police say that the condition of one of them is serious. Rathgama Police is conducting further investigations."
      ],
